modName: Xander Male Dunmer Preset for ECE
descriptionHtml:
I made this ECE preset because I don't like the angular faces of elves in TES.  It's basically the last stock male preset for Bretons modified and then adapted for Dumner use.  I made it for myself but I figure I'd share it cause why not.  (Also there are so many female presets going up that a male one might be nice to see).

[size=4]Version 1.01 Now includes CharGen meshes and textures, RaceMenu users can import the head mesh and it should work just fine!
[/size]
[u]REQUIRED FOR EXACT LOOK
[/u]Better Males (Underwear Slip) 
Smooth Male Body (Nevernude with underwear)
Fine Face Textures
Brows by Hvergelmir
Beards by Hvergelmir
Northborn Scars
The Eyes of Beauty (Elven Edition)
KS Hairdos - Renewal (ChainReaction)

You can use different textures/body/hair if you wish however the mods above are what I used.

[u]INSTALLATION

[/u]Install to C:\Users\(PC Name)\Documents\My Games\Skyrim\CME_save

You may change the slot if you already have a saved preset on 3

[u]CREDITS
[/u][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?]Enhanced Character Edit [/url]by TK & the ECE Team
